query:

  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  requestId INT NOT NULL,
  imageUrl TEXT NOT NULL,
  originalFilename VARCHAR(255),
  fileSize INT,
  mimeType VARCHAR(100),
  uploadedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
